    <main class="container">
        <div class="section">
            <h1>Welcome to Qapture!</h1>
            <p>Qapture is the simplest way to collect, share, and relive your favorite moments. Whether it's a spontaneous outing or a family gathering, Qapture makes it easy to bring all your photos and videos together, accessible to everyone who matters.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>How It Works</h2>
            <p><strong>Effortless, Unified, Timeless</strong></p>
            <ol>
                <li><strong>Capture with Ease:</strong> Snap photos or videos, and Qapture automatically organizes them for you.</li>
                <li><strong>Instant Sharing:</strong> Share a unique QR code with friends and family to instantly gather their moments.</li>
                <li><strong>Relive the Good Times:</strong> Enjoy all your shared moments in one beautifully organized digital album.</li>
            </ol>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>Key Features</h2>
            <p><strong>Qapture offers features that enhance your experience:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Automatic Organization:</strong> No more scattered photos. Qapture keeps everything neatly in one place.</li>
                <li><strong>Inclusive Sharing:</strong> Everyone can contribute and access shared moments, ensuring nothing gets missed.</li>
                <li><strong>Universal Accessibility:</strong> Access your moments on any device, anywhere, anytime.</li>
                <li><strong>Always Secure:</strong> Your memories are protected with advanced security measures.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>Benefits</h2>
            <p><strong>Why Choose Qapture?</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Never Lose a Moment:</strong> Qapture ensures your moments are never accidentally deleted or lost.</li>
                <li><strong>Simplified Sharing:</strong> Share your memories effortlessly, with everything in one place.</li>
                <li><strong>Accessible to Everyone:</strong> Qapture is easy to use for everyone, regardless of tech-savviness.</li>
                <li><strong>Cost-Effective:</strong> Save on storage fees and avoid juggling multiple apps.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="section testimonials">
            <h2>Testimonials</h2>
            <p><em>“Qapture saved me from the chaos of organizing my photos. Everything is beautifully arranged and easy to access.”</em> - Sarah M.</p>
            <p><em>“I love how I can share moments with my family so effortlessly. It feels like we’re always connected.”</em> - Daniel T.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section faq">
            <h2>FAQs</h2>
            <dl>
                <dt>Q: How does it work?</dt>
                <dd>A: Just capture your moments as usual; Qapture takes care of the rest.</dd>

                <dt>Q: Is there a limit to the number of photos or videos I can upload?</dt>
                <dd>A: No limits. Your memories are unlimited.</dd>

                <dt>Q: How secure is Qapture?</dt>
                <dd>A: We use cutting-edge security to keep your memories safe.</dd>

                <dt>Q: Can I access my photos on multiple devices?</dt>
                <dd>A: Yes, your memories are available wherever you are.</dd>

                <dt>Q: Is Qapture free?</dt>
                <dd>A: Enjoy our core features for free, with premium options for more capabilities.</dd>
            </dl>
